    <div class="col-12 com-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="service-card">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ddo3vrwcb/image/upload/v1676014114/publications_il2uzf.png" />
            <h3>Publications</h3>
            <p>Share your work with the world and receive feedback and support.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 com-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="service-card">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ddo3vrwcb/image/upload/v1676014157/save_nzev5w.png" />
            <h3>Save for Later</h3>
            <p>Keep track of your favorite pieces and come back to them later.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 com-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="service-card">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ddo3vrwcb/image/upload/v1676014189/group_qx5opz.png" />
            <h3>Groups</h3>
            <p>Join or create groups with like-minded artists.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 com-md-6 col-lg-3">
        <div class="service-card">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ddo3vrwcb/image/upload/v1676014224/direct_hzlwjh.png" />
            <h3>Direct Chats</h3>
            <p>Connect with other artists and have private conversations.</p>
